INSERT INTO `wp_options` VALUES("561", "_transient_wp_travel_engine_store_addons_list", "{\n    \"products\": [\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 79,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-fixed-starting-dates\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Fixed Starting Dates\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-01-10 11:38:32\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2023-09-21 13:39:10\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=79\",\n                \"permalink\": \"\\/plugins\\/trip-fixed-starting-dates\\/\",\n                \"content\": \"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Trip Fixed Starting Dates add-on lets you easily schedule specific dates and times for your trips, ensuring travellers book only when it\'s convenient for you.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">How you can benefit from it:&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Add fixed departure dates and times, and enjoy peace of mind knowing that bookings can only be made on the dates you\'ve set.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Easily assign a specific number of seats for each departure date, ensuring accurate and streamlined seat management.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Display all trips with departure dates in a single location, enabling travellers to search swiftly and book trips according to their availability.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Empower travellers to mix departure dates with other factors like cost, trip type, and destination, facilitating faster and more tailored searches for booking the perfect trip.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Quickly show trips with the next departure dates on the search page, making it easy for travellers to see and book upcoming trips.&nbsp;<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Use recurring dates to avoid manual entry and save loads of time.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ul>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">1. Unlock flexibility and convenience: set specific booking dates and times!<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127653,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/06\\/set-specific-dates-and-times.png\\\" alt=\\\"set specific booking dates and times\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127653\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Set specific booking dates and times tailored to your customers\' convenience.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can allow them to plan their adventures easily by choosing the precise departure dates and times that suit their schedules. This level of flexibility ensures a seamless booking experience and enhances customer satisfaction.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">2. Effortless recurring time: simplify trip scheduling!<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127659,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/Recurring-time-feature.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127659\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Managing trips that repeat on specific days or intervals has never been easier.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Whether it\'s a weekly excursion, a monthly getaway, or any other pattern you desire, you can streamline your trip scheduling and offer recurring trips without any hassle.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">3. Ensure exclusivity with managed available spots!<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127684,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/seat-management.png\\\" alt=\\\"Ensure exclusivity with managed available spots\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127684\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Create a sense of exclusivity and urgency by managing the available spots for each fixed departure date.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can set the number of spots available for booking, ensuring personalized experiences for your customers. By showcasing limited availability, you\'ll generate excitement and encourage early bookings, maximizing your revenue potential.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">4. Sort trips according to departure dates to highlight upcoming trips<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127672,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/Sort-trip-according-to-departure-date.png\\\" alt=\\\"Sort trip according to departure date\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127672\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Make the trip selection process easier by allowing users to easily sort trips by departure date on the trip listing page.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Each individual trip card on the trip listing page displays the next departure date, providing instant visibility and making trip selection a breeze.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">5. Display Fixed Starting Dates from all your trips in a single page&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127697,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/Display-Trip-Fixed-Starting-Dates-anywhere.png\\\" alt=\\\"Display Trip Fixed Starting Dates anywhere\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127697\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>By simply implementing the powerful [WTE_TRIPS_FIXED_STARTING_DATES] shortcode, you can effortlessly display fixed starting dates from all your trips.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>This feature provides a comprehensive overview of available departure dates, giving your customers the flexibility to choose the perfect time to book their trip.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">6. Display Trip Fixed Starting Dates anywhere<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Using simple shortcodes, you can easily change the position or display the fixed starting dates anywhere on your website.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Whether it\'s on the homepage, trip pages, or even in blog posts, you have the freedom to showcase the availability calendar and capture the attention of potential customers.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">7. Minimal configuration for maximum impact!<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127677,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/Minimal-configuration-for-maximum-impact.gif\\\" alt=\\\"Trip Fixed Starting Dates setting \\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127677\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>We understand that time is of the essence when managing a travel booking website. That\'s why the Trip Fixed Starting Dates Addon is designed with minimal configuration in mind.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>With a user-friendly interface and intuitive settings, you can quickly and easily set up your desired fixed starting dates and times, allowing you to focus on what matters most - delivering exceptional travel experiences to your customers.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Video Tutorial<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:html -->\\n<iframe width=\\\"790\\\" height=\\\"444\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/nv9mABmEvCk\\\" title=\\\"Trip Fixed Starting Dates Add-On |  WP Travel Engine Tutorial\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allow=\\\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\\\" allowfullscreen><\\/iframe>\\n<!-- \\/wp:html -->\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This extension allows travel agencies and tour operators to show trip fixed starting dates and number of space available for booking.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/08\\/Trip-Fixed-Starting-Dates.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"dow