le popups.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Not only does this give your website an air of credibility, but it also builds trust with potential customers.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><iframe title=\\\"YouTube video player\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/wQwvD0RUHuU\\\" width=\\\"790\\\" height=\\\"444\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"allowfullscreen\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Key Features<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Social Proof Dashboard<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Social Proof Dashboard lists all of your notifications in one place and provides a breakdown of how many people have viewed them and clicked through notifications. You can also track the click-through rate for each notification to see how effective they are at driving bookings.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Total View Count: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It shows the number of times your notification has been viewed.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Click Count:<\\/b> <span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It displays the number of times users have clicked on the notification.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Click-Through Rate (CTR):<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">&nbsp; <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It shows the rate of clicks by its views in percentage.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ul>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Notification Type<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can create three different types of notifications using the Social Proof add-on.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Trip Booking Notification: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This notification is displayed when someone books a trip.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Trip Enquiry Notification:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> It pops up when someone makes an inquiry about a trip.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Trip Review Notification:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> This notification is displayed when someone leaves a review for a trip.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ul>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Notification Settings<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With Social Proof\\u2019s extensive customizable options, you can manage and control how and when your notifications are displayed. These are the settings you can adjust:<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Notification Type: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can select the type of notification you want to add.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Notification Styles: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can pick the design style for your notification.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Content Editing: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can add content or create a template for the notification pop-up. You can use the existing tags to display customer-specific information.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Show Booking of:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> You can choose to display the booking notification for all trips or for the selected trips on your website.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Show on: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It lets you display the notifications either across all the pages of your website or only on the Single Trip page.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Display for: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can choose to display the notification either for everyone or just for logged-in users.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Position:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> It allows you to select the position for the notification popup.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Notification Size:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> This allows you to define the maximum width of the notification in pixels.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Mobile Visibility:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> Enabling this option hides the notification on small screen-size devices.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Delay Before First Notification:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> You can set the time in seconds after which you want to display the notification once a site has loaded.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Display For:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> It lets you enter the timeframe for each notification to display.<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><b>Delay Between: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 